_:N7d27ee365b10494ea992ffd5546a5054 <http://schema.org/description> "VisitBritain (VB) is the national tourism agency, responsible for marketing Britain worldwide and developing Britain’s visitor economy. It works with UK Trade & Investment as well as airlines, travel operators, global brands and the official tourism bodies for London, England, Scotland and Wales. VB is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
